source:
TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_SEQ_00 Quest Sync
The honest alchemist needs help.
target:
TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_SEQ_00 Quest Sync
The honest alchemist needs help.

source: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_TODO_01<tab>Speak with the honest alchemist again.
target: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_TODO_01<tab>Speak with the honest alchemist again.

source: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_TODO_02<tab>Retrieve the goods from the water.
target: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_TODO_02<tab>Retrieve the goods from the water.

source: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_HONESTALCHEMIST_000_001<tab>You've come by at the perfect time, adventurer! Could you help me find someone? One of my colleagues went to receive a delivery and hasn't come back. I'm worried something might have happened...
target: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_HONESTALCHEMIST_000_001<tab>You've come by at the perfect time, adventurer! Could you help me find someone? One of my colleagues went to receive a delivery and hasn't come back. I'm worried something might have happened...

source: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_HONESTALCHEMIST_000_002<tab>Oh, thank you. He went to Yedlihmad, so let's start by looking around the aetheryte there.
target: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_HONESTALCHEMIST_000_002<tab>Oh, thank you. He went to Yedlihmad, so let's start by looking around the aetheryte there.

source: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_HONESTALCHEMIST_000_003<tab>I've been asking around about my colleague, and someone claims to have seen him setting out from port in a small boat.
target: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_HONESTALCHEMIST_000_003<tab>I've been asking around about my colleague, and someone claims to have seen him setting out from port in a small boat.

source: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_HONESTALCHEMIST_000_004<tab>Maybe he loaded the shipment onto it and headed back. In which case, we must have just missed him. I hope that's all that happened...
target: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_HONESTALCHEMIST_000_004<tab>Maybe he loaded the shipment onto it and headed back. In which case, we must have just missed him. I hope that's all that happened...

source: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_HONESTALCHEMIST_000_005<tab>Well, let's head back to the Great Work. We should keep an eye on the shoreline on our way back just in case.
target: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_HONESTALCHEMIST_000_005<tab>Well, let's head back to the Great Work. We should keep an eye on the shoreline on our way back just in case.

source: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_HONESTALCHEMIST_000_007<tab>Oh no! His boat must have capsized!
target: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_HONESTALCHEMIST_000_007<tab>Oh no! His boat must have capsized!

source: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_COLLEAGUEALCHEMIST_000_008<tab>I... I loaded...everything...on the boat to bring back... But something hit us, and...
target: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_COLLEAGUEALCHEMIST_000_008<tab>I... I loaded...everything...on the boat to bring back... But something hit us, and...

source: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_COLLEAGUEALCHEMIST_000_009<tab>I managed to swim to safety, but the cargo... I'm so sorry...
target: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_COLLEAGUEALCHEMIST_000_009<tab>I managed to swim to safety, but the cargo... I'm so sorry...

source: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_HONESTALCHEMIST_000_010<tab>Forget the cargo! All that matters is you're all right. We'll just have to do without the sunken goods.
target: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_HONESTALCHEMIST_000_010<tab>Forget the cargo! All that matters is you're all right. We'll just have to do without the sunken goods.

source: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_A1_000_001<tab>Shall I retrieve them for you?
target: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_A1_000_001<tab>Shall I retrieve them for you?

source: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_A1_000_002<tab>Looks like the perfect opportunity to practice my underwater breathing technique.
target: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_A1_000_002<tab>Looks like the perfect opportunity to practice my underwater breathing technique.

source: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_COLLEAGUEALCHEMIST_000_012<tab>Thank you... There were five articles in all... Some of them sunk...but some float.
target: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_COLLEAGUEALCHEMIST_000_012<tab>Thank you... There were five articles in all... Some of them sunk...but some float.

source: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_HONESTALCHEMIST_000_013<tab>I'm sorry to leave all of this to you, but I need to get him home before his condition worsens. We'll head back to the Great Work first, so come meet us when you're done.
target: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_HONESTALCHEMIST_000_013<tab>I'm sorry to leave all of this to you, but I need to get him home before his condition worsens. We'll head back to the Great Work first, so come meet us when you're done.

source: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_HONESTALCHEMIST_000_014<tab>You made it back! If you're worried about my colleague, he's fine. Just resting after clearing out the water in his lungs. I gave him some chai and he went right to sleep.
target: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_HONESTALCHEMIST_000_014<tab>You made it back! If you're worried about my colleague, he's fine. Just resting after clearing out the water in his lungs. I gave him some chai and he went right to sleep.

source: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_HONESTALCHEMIST_000_015<tab>You managed to retrieve all the lost cargo? Incredible! These are valuable weapons imported from Vylbrand. They just need a few alchemic finishing touches before they're complete.
target: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_HONESTALCHEMIST_000_015<tab>You managed to retrieve all the lost cargo? Incredible! These are valuable weapons imported from Vylbrand. They just need a few alchemic finishing touches before they're complete.

source: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_HONESTALCHEMIST_000_016<tab>From here, they'll head off to the hands of the Radz<var 1F /var>at<var 1F /var>Han warriors to help protect the order. Thank you for everything, adventurer.
target: TEXT_AKTKZA026_04205_HONESTALCHEMIST_000_016<tab>From here, they'll head off to the hands of the Radz<var 1F /var>at<var 1F /var>Han warriors to help protect the order. Thank you for everything, adventurer.
